[3] China (Shanghai) H7N9
Date: Fri 5 Feb 2016
Source: FIC (Flu in China) [edited]
http://www.flu.org.cn/en/news-18509.html


China: Shanghai reported a human H7N9 case
------------------------------------------
Shanghai MCHFP announced a human H7N9 case on 5 Feb 2016. The patient, male, 66-year-old, confirmed on 5 Feb 2016, is now in hospital for treatment.

