[Note that the case numbers in FluTracker are continuous since 2013. They include 2 additional cases not accounted for in other reports above. It is difficult to reconcile numbers between different reports since cases are not always well described. Also, whether exposure is primary or secondary is not always reported.

Maps of China can be found at http://www.sacu.org/maps/provmap.png and https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=4002127,155. - Mod.LK]
